    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Check if you can claim back Statutory Sick Pay paid to employees due to coronavirus (COVID-19)
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-third">
      <nav role="navigation" class="gem-c-translation-nav gem-c-translation-nav " aria-label="Translations">
    <ul class="gem-c-translation-nav__list">
        <li class="gem-c-translation-nav__list-item">
            <span lang="en">English</span>
        </li>
        <li class="gem-c-translation-nav__list-item">
            <a hreflang="cy" lang="cy" rel="alternate" class="gem-c-translation-nav__link " href="/guidance/claim-back-statutory-sick-pay-paid-to-employees-due-to-coronavirus-covid-19.cy">Cymraeg</a>
        </li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  </div>

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">If you're an employer, find out if you can use the Coronavirus Statutory Sick Pay Rebate Scheme to claim back employees' coronavirus-related Statutory Sick Pay (SSP).</p>

  </div>
</div>

